import React from 'react'

import constants from '../constants'

function Movie(props) {
    //const {API_URL} = constants 
    const API_URL  = 'http://192.168.0.206:8080'
    const {id} = props

    return <video id="videoPlayer" 
            controls width="620" 
            height="400" 
            src={API_URL + '/list/'+id} 
            type="video/mp4">
        </video>
}

export default Movie
